data.Name: Galactic Explorers
data.Bio: German prog/electronic band. Released an album of proto-ambience in 1972. Synthesizer [Minimoog], Organ [Hammond] - Johannes Lutz Synthesizer, Guitar, Electronics - Holst Seisert Synthesizer, Percussion, Organ [Electric] - Reinhard Karwatsky Actually this is bogus kraut. "The album is not listed in any kraut rock discographical guide, because it is NOT a krautrock recording but a hoax adout an hypothetical label "Pyramid". The session had been recorded during the early 90ies by people connected with the group SUNDIAL and the Acme label. Read more on Last.fm
